AI Campus Navigation System

An AI-powered campus navigation system that helps students, faculty, and visitors easily find locations within a university or college campus. This project integrates maps, search functionality, and AI-driven suggestions to make campus navigation seamless.

📌 Features

🔎 Search by Location – Quickly find classrooms, labs, libraries, hostels, or administrative offices.

🧭 Path Guidance – Provides shortest routes between two locations on campus.

🗺️ Interactive Map – Visual campus map with clickable markers.

🤖 AI Assistance – Suggests nearby facilities (canteens, washrooms, departments, etc.).

📱 User-Friendly Interface – Simple and intuitive UI for all users.

🏗️ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (React/VanillaJS – update based on your code)

Backend: Python (Flask/Django/FastAPI) / Node.js (update accordingly)

Database: SQLite / MySQL / MongoDB (update accordingly)

AI/ML: NLP model for search & recommendation (if implemented)

Maps: Custom campus map (image/graph) or Google Maps API

⚙️ Installation & Setup

Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/your-username/ai-campus-navigation-system.git
cd ai-campus-navigation-system


Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt   # For Python backend
# OR
npm install   # If using Node.js


Run the project

python app.py   # Flask/Django backend
# OR
npm start       # Node.js backend


Access in browser

http://localhost:5000  # or the port mentioned

📂 Project Structure
ai-campus-navigation-system/
│── frontend/        # UI code (HTML/CSS/JS or React)
│── backend/         # API & logic (Python/Node.js)
│── database/        # Campus location data
│── docs/            # Project documentation
│── README.md        # Project overview
│── requirements.txt # Python dependencies
│── package.json     # Node.js dependencies (if applicable)

